value: content=This resort in Puerto Princesa offers two type of rooms which are: first the "Casita" (maximum adults: 4, maximum children: 1) and it is equipped with air conditioning, minibar, private toilet and bath, queen bed, hot and cold shower. The second room offered is: "Pavilion" (maximum adults: 10, maximum children: 1) and it is equipped with private toilet and bath, electric fan, hot and cold shower. Some of its facilities and services are tree house and hammock, floating veranda for cocktails and Al fresci dining areas.
